desc: Anna Webb is an expert dog trainer, behaviourist and nutritionist. She is a leading authority in the UK who appears frequently on Television and Radio. She is the host of the popular podcast A Dog's Life with Anna Webb. For advice, training and product recommendations for you and your dog, consult Anna Webb

layout.text: I believe all animals, especially dogs, make us Human
With my advice on training, behaviour and nutrition, I will help you develop a line of communication with your dog built on focus and trust
